      "updated": 1777311197268,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "vm module logic:\nProfile (vm_type)\ncpu count logic (overrides or use profile)\nmemory gb logic (overrides or use profile)\ndisk0 size logic (override or use profile)\nadditional disks logic (map unity numbers, override if\nprovided in build file)\ncloud-init metadata build from vars\ncloud-init userdata build from vars\n\nBUILD!",
      "fontSize": 22.688408941799427,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "KVQUcPfhsP4hlwRk-g_Kz",
      "originalText": "vm module logic:\nProfile (vm_type)\ncpu count logic (overrides or use profile)\nmemory gb logic (overrides or use profile)\ndisk0 size logic (override or use profile)\nadditional disks logic (map unity numbers, override if provided in build file)\ncloud-init metadata build from vars\ncloud-init userdata build from vars\n\nBUILD!",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
